language ESSENCE 1.2.0
$ prob025.essence: Lam's Problem
$ Problem details available at http://www.csplib.org/prob/prob025/
$ 06 September 2007
$

letting Index be type of size 111

find m : matrix indexed by [Index,Index] of bool

such that
    forAll r : Index . ((sum c : Index . not(m[r,c])) = 11),
    forAll c : Index . ((sum r : Index . not(m[r,c])) = 11),
    forAll r1,r2 : Index . (
        (r1 != r2) => (
            (sum c : Index . not(m[r1,c] \/ m[r2,c])) = 1
        )
    )
